This repository contains the public documentation, manifests, SDK examples, and
integration helpers for the Gapup MCP (Model Context Protocol) server hosted at
https://mcp.gapup.io.

THE SERVER IMPLEMENTATION ITSELF IS NOT INCLUDED IN THIS REPOSITORY.
The server source code, including tool prompts, persona definitions, output
schemas, data fetchers, and orchestration logic, is proprietary and not
distributed under this or any open-source license.

USAGE TERMS:

1. The hosted API at https://mcp.gapup.io is provided under the Gapup Terms of
   Service available at https://hub.gapup.io/terms.

2. Free tier: 100 calls per calendar month per API key, no credit card required.
   Key issuance subject to Terms of Service.

3. Paid usage: via x402 micro-payments (USDC / EURC) per the public pricing grid
   (T0 $0.002 → T6 $1.50). See docs/PRICING.md for details.

4. The contents of this repository (README, manifests, docs/, client/) MAY be:
   - Read and referenced freely
   - Used to configure third-party MCP clients
   - Quoted with attribution in articles, talks, technical posts

5. The contents of this repository MAY NOT be:
   - Redistributed in modified form claiming to be the Gapup MCP
   - Used to operate a competing service under the Gapup name or branding
   - Used to reverse-engineer or clone the server implementation

6. The manifests (smithery.yaml, server.json) reference the hosted Gapup
   service. Forking these to point to a different endpoint while preserving the
   Gapup branding is expressly forbidden.

7. SDK examples in client/ are provided for integration illustration only.
   They are not warranted or supported beyond their educational purpose.

